  title = {Looking into the {{faintEst WIth MUSE}} ({{LEWIS}}): {{Exploring}} the Nature of Ultra-Diffuse Galaxies in the {{Hydra-I}} Cluster {{IV}}. {{A}} Study of the {{Globular Cluster}} Population in Four {{UDGs}}},
